    "patch_code": "public double chiS square(long[] observed, double[] expected)\n   \n    return chiS square( observed, expected, true);\n    \nprivate double chiS square(long[] observed, double[] expected, boolean resscale)\n{\n    if (!res scale) {\n        for ( int i = 0; i < observed. length; i++) {\n            if (!is positive( expected[i])) {\n                return chiS square( observed, expected, true);\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    double sumSq = 0.0d;\n    double dev = 0.0d;\n    for (int i = 0; i < observed.length; i++) {\n        dev = observed[i]- expected[i];\n        sumSq +=  dev * dev / expected[i];\n    }\n    return sumSq;\n}",
